  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Pinball Dream</i> is an 80s arcade-style pinball and brick-breaker game. </strong>  If you want to relax and relieve stress, this game is perfect for you. Get amazing power-ups, break all the blocks, and defeat the boss! The classic pinball mechanism has been transformed into a breathtaking arcade experience. Drop everything and play \"<strong><i>Pinball Dream</i></strong>\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3997910/extras/1640428e741f01a77d3cbd5e81476099.poster.avif?t=1774092620\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3997910/extras/1640428e741f01a77d3cbd5e81476099.webm?t=1774092620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3997910/extras/1640428e741f01a77d3cbd5e81476099.mp4?t=1774092620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each section is light neon glow. You will loved the retro-future vibe of each exciting area. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3997910/extras/eca5108b7e795fb5f734c8e6120a2b99.poster.avif?t=1774092620\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3997910/extras/eca5108b7e795fb5f734c8e6120a2b99.webm?t=1774092620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3997910/extras/eca5108b7e795fb5f734c8e6120a2b99.mp4?t=1774092620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
